11#ifndef MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTCP_PACKET_TMMBR_H_
12#define MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTCP_PACKET_TMMBR_H_
13
14#include <vector>
15
16#include "modules/rtp_rtcp/source/rtcp_packet/rtpfb.h"
17#include "modules/rtp_rtcp/source/rtcp_packet/tmmb_item.h"
18
19namespace webrtc {
20namespace rtcp {
21class CommonHeader;
22
23// Temporary Maximum Media Stream Bit Rate Request (TMMBR).
24// RFC 5104, Section 4.2.1.
25class Tmmbr : public Rtpfb {
26 public:
27 static constexpr uint8_t kFeedbackMessageType = 3;
28
29 Tmmbr();
30 ~Tmmbr() override;
31
32 // Parse assumes header is already parsed and validated.
33 bool Parse(const CommonHeader& packet);
34
35 void AddTmmbr(const TmmbItem& item);
36
37 const std::vector<TmmbItem>& requests() const { return items_; }
38
39 size_t BlockLength() const override;
40
41 bool Create(uint8_t* packet,
42 size_t* index,
43 size_t max_length,
44 PacketReadyCallback callback) const override;
45
46 private:
47 // Media ssrc is unused, shadow base class setter.
48 void SetMediaSsrc(uint32_t ssrc);
49
50 std::vector<TmmbItem> items_;
51};
52} // namespace rtcp
53} // namespace webrtc
54#endif // MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTCP_PACKET_TMMBR_H_
